#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:84
msgid "Several companies can be managed within the same database. Each company has its :doc:`chart of accounts <accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>`, but it is possible to share accounts between them for scenarios in which such a configuration would be required. Users can then access several companies but only work on a single company's accounting at a time."
