msgid "In the :guilabel:`Journal Items to reconcile` list view, click :guilabel:`Auto-Reconcile` next to the receivable or payable account (or a specific contact's group of journal items in that account)."
msgstr "В списке :guilabel:`Проводки для сверки` нажмите :guilabel:`Автосверка` рядом с дебиторской или кредиторской задолженностью (или группой проводок для конкретного контакта)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:226
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Reconcile automatically` window, click :guilabel:`Reconcile`."
msgstr "В окне :guilabel:`Автоматическая сверка` нажмите :guilabel:`Свернуть`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:235
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Reconcile Automatically` window, set the :guilabel:`Reconcile` field depending on how you want to match journal items:"
