#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:279
msgid "The invoices or bills are then marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until the bank transactions are :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with the payments."
msgstr "Счета или накладные помечаются как :guilabel:`В оплате` до :doc:`сверки <bank/reconciliation>` банковских транзакций с платежами."

