#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:126
msgid "For more information on document digitization and :abbr:`IAPs (in-app purchases)`, refer to the :doc:`In-app purchase (IAP) <../../essentials/in_app_purchase>` documentation."
msgstr "Подробнее об оцифровке документов и :abbr:`IAP (внутриигровых покупках)` см. в документации :doc:`Внутриигровые покупки (IAP) <../../essentials/in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/log_expenses.rst:130
