#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:55
msgid "Regardless of customer relations, bankruptcy, or dissolution, Odoo can provide access to transaction and digital voucher details to former clients for six years (see :ref:`localizations/denmark/data-lifecycle`)."
msgstr "Независимо от отношений с клиентом, банкротства или ликвидации, Odoo может предоставлять бывшим клиентам доступ к деталям транзакций и цифровых ваучеров в течение шести лет (см. :ref:`localizations/denmark/data-lifecycle`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:59
msgid "Automated data export and secure storage"
msgstr "Автоматизированный экспорт данных и безопасное хранение"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:61
msgid "Odoo Accounting implements no automatic deletion or archival of recorded transactions, so if a company has been recording transactions for six years, the six years of history are preserved in the Odoo Accounting database."
