#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:689
msgid "The *Ecuadorian Module for Point of Sale* adds two new fields to the contact creation form: :guilabel:`Identification Type` and :guilabel:`Tax ID`."
msgstr "Модуль *Ecuadorian Module for Point of Sale* добавляет два новых поля в форму создания контакта: :guilabel:`Тип идентификации` и :guilabel:`Налоговый идентификатор`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:693
msgid "As the identification number length differs depending on the identification type, Odoo automatically checks the :guilabel:`Tax ID` field upon saving the contact form. To manually ensure the length is correct, know that the :guilabel:`RUC` and :guilabel:`Citizenship` types require 13 and 10 digits, respectively."
