msgid "In the United States, tax rates and what is considered taxable vary by jurisdiction. Default *Sales* and *Purchase* taxes are created automatically when the Odoo *Accounting* application is installed. To manage existing or configure additional taxes, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes`."
